WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.667
How to use Folia — edit any PDF in five simple steps.

00:00:02.667 --> 00:00:07.667
Step 1: Open your PDF.

00:00:07.667 --> 00:00:13.667
Step 2: Reorder, rotate, and delete pages.

00:00:13.667 --> 00:00:20.333
Step 3: Highlight, draw, and add notes.

00:00:20.333 --> 00:00:25.667
Step 4: Fill in forms and add your signature.

00:00:25.667 --> 00:00:29.667
Step 5: Save your edited PDF.

00:00:29.667 --> 00:00:34.000
Folia keeps your files 100% private — they never leave your computer.
